1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,787
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 4=

11
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:00,799
Su Wubing!

12
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:04,239
Get out of here!

13
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,640
All of you, move!

14
00:01:11,319 --> 00:01:12,519
A bunch of useless fools.

15
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,920
Go apologize to everyone

16
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,120
you just knocked over.

17
00:01:20,439 --> 00:01:20,959
And

18
00:01:21,879 --> 00:01:23,239
clean up the hospital.

19
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:25,799
Yes, yes.

20
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,120
Dr. Ye.

21
00:01:35,879 --> 00:01:36,480
Are you alright?

22
00:01:37,519 --> 00:01:38,319
I'm fine.

23
00:01:44,319 --> 00:01:45,799
(Is this still Su Wubing?)

24
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:48,239
(He seems like
a completely different person.)

25
00:02:06,519 --> 00:02:07,400
(In this life,)

26
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,639
(Fang Tian, Adopted Sister)
(thanks to her for taking care of my mom.)

27
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,199
(My spiritual power's too weak.)

28
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,800
(I need to start cultivating quickly.)

29
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,560
(But I'm afraid)

30
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:36,199
(this mortal body can't handle it.)

31
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,560
Wubing, you're back.

32
00:02:51,199 --> 00:02:52,759
How's Mom doing lately?

33
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:57,080
Not looking good.

34
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,319
She's been unconscious for days.

35
00:03:01,439 --> 00:03:03,879
I got a talisman,

36
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:05,800
and drew the best fortune.

37
00:03:06,439 --> 00:03:07,879
Mom will definitely pull through.

38
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:16,680
Mom, you're awake!

39
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:20,159
Wubing, mom really woke up!

40
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:29,400
(She recovered so fast)

41
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,479
(and didn't even need surgery.)

42
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:35,199
Maybe Wubing's got superpowers.

43
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,639
mom got better when he came back.

44
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:41,439
Ma'ma, you can go home now.

45
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,919
Take care of yourself.

46
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,240
Dr. Ye.

47
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:46,560
Thanks for all your help these days.

48
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,639
It's my duty.

49
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,960
Your health is all that matters.

50
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:54,240
Besides, your son helped me too.

51
00:03:54,599 --> 00:03:56,400
So don't mention it.

52
00:03:57,439 --> 00:03:58,639
He helped you?

53
00:03:58,719 --> 00:04:00,240
Mom.

54
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,080
Let's go check out

55
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:02,919
and take a walk.

56
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:04,360
Wubing, I'll take Mom.

57
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,319
Everything's packed.

58
00:04:05,719 --> 00:04:06,400
Just take it later.

59
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,319
Let's go, Mom.

60
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:08,879
Take care.

61
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,680
You're...

62
00:04:16,879 --> 00:04:18,639
not some mysterious expert, are you?

63
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,639
Maybe I'm overthinking.

64
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,680
Your mom recovered way too fast.

65
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:29,879
That's thanks to your care.

66
00:04:35,959 --> 00:04:36,959
Here's my card.

67
00:04:37,439 --> 00:04:38,879
Call me if your mother needs anything.

68
00:04:41,519 --> 00:04:42,839
Even if nothing comes up,

69
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,720
you can still call me.

70
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:47,759
Wubing.

71
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:54,399
Dr. Ye, we're checking out.

72
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,079
We won't trouble you again.

73
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:57,319
Alright.

74
00:04:59,079 --> 00:04:59,720
You two talk.

75
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,279
I'll go with Mom.

76
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,000
Does he

77
00:05:07,759 --> 00:05:08,680
have a girlfriend?

78
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,319
I don't know.

79
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:13,399
You two aren't siblings, right?

80
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,000
Grab the stuff.

81
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:21,720
Got it.

82
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,120
Wubing.

83
00:05:46,279 --> 00:05:47,680
Are we really living here now?

84
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,160
Why,

85
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:50,319
don't like it?

86
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:52,560
Love it.

87
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:54,480
I'll set up the room now.

88
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,040
Mom.

89
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:01,199
Wubing, be honest with me.

90
00:06:01,759 --> 00:06:03,959
Where did this house come from?

91
00:06:05,839 --> 00:06:07,199
It's a friend's.

92
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,480
She said it'd sit empty anyway.

93
00:06:09,759 --> 00:06:11,040
She said we could stay here

94
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,279
so you can recover.

95
00:06:13,319 --> 00:06:15,199
By the way, her place is next door.

96
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:19,680
Good.

97
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:23,759
Wubing.

98
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:26,560
What do you think of Tian?

99
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:29,600
Mom.

100
00:06:30,199 --> 00:06:31,680
I've always treated her like a sister.

101
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,319
I know.

102
00:06:34,199 --> 00:06:36,680
But you two aren't blood siblings.

103
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:40,319
She's sensible and sweet.

104
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,920
You two grew up together...

105
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,480
Mom.

106
00:06:45,759 --> 00:06:46,920
That's my private matter.

107
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,199
Don't worry about it.

108
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:55,920
What's wrong?

109
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:56,920
Wubing.

110
00:06:58,199 --> 00:06:59,240
There's a spider.

111
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,480
Still scared of spiders

112
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,480
at this age?

113
00:07:12,199 --> 00:07:13,600
Where're the talismans I got you before?

114
00:07:18,959 --> 00:07:19,759
Here.

115
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:27,920
From now on, carry these with you.

116
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,199
If danger shows up,

117
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:30,560
I'll be there.

118
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:33,959
Wubing.

119
00:07:37,199 --> 00:07:40,519
What did mom just tell you?

120
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:44,240
Nothing.

121
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:47,680
Did she say we...

122
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,680
The Lin family invites Mr. Su over.

123
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,079
Mr. Lin.

124
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,680
My savior is here.

125
00:08:01,759 --> 00:08:02,920
Please accept my bow.

126
00:08:03,319 --> 00:08:04,079
Mr. Lin.

127
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,079
No need for formalities.

128
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,079
Just helping out.

129
00:08:17,319 --> 00:08:19,920
Stop calling me "Mr. Lin".

130
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,079
I'm older than you.

131
00:08:21,079 --> 00:08:22,240
Call me "Uncle Lin".

132
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:24,920
Older?

133
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:26,639
What...

134
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:29,839
Are you older than me?

135
00:08:33,879 --> 00:08:34,519
Uncle Lin.

136
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:39,480
The Lin Group has weathered
decades of ups and downs.

137
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:42,240
It looks good on the surface
but is full of risks.

138
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:44,080
I had this serious illness,

139
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:47,240
and Ningxue held the family
together alone.

140
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,519
Not easy at all.

141
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:52,919
Do you want me to help Ningxue?

142
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:58,080
With the Gu family watching closely,

143
00:08:58,519 --> 00:09:01,519
I can tell you're no ordinary person.

144
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:04,519
So I have a bold request.

145
00:09:06,039 --> 00:09:06,799
Uncle Lin.

146
00:09:10,039 --> 00:09:11,320
If you don't mind,

147
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,639
I'd like to entrust Ningxue to you.

148
00:09:14,799 --> 00:09:16,639
Outsiders see you as marrying in,

149
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:19,679
but really, our family's lucky
to have you.

150
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:20,919
Alright.

151
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,039
You mean that?

152
00:09:22,519 --> 00:09:23,519
I won't go back on my word.

153
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:25,679
Then I'll be counting
on you from now on.

154
00:10:28,677 --> 00:10:32,780
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

155
00:10:32,780 --> 00:10:37,500
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

156
00:10:37,500 --> 00:10:42,380
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

157
00:10:42,380 --> 00:10:47,500
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

158
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:51,900
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

159
00:10:51,900 --> 00:10:56,580
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

160
00:10:56,580 --> 00:11:01,980
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

161
00:11:01,980 --> 00:11:08,007
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪
